<bioghist altrender="history" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
	<head>Historical Note</head>
	<p>This organization is composed of male descendants of veterans of the Union Army in the Civil War. The organization was involved in marking the graves of Civil War veterans, ensuring proper observance of national holidays, and the care and upkeep of Civil War Memorials.</p>
</bioghist>
<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
	<head>Scope and Content</head>
	<p>Records include correspondence, financial records and pamphlets.</p>
</scopecontent>
